{"text_id":4856,"tokens":["Galaxy"," clustering"," constraints"," on"," deviations"," from"," Newtonian"," gravity"," at"," cosmological"," scales"," II",":"," Pert","urb","ative"," and"," numerical"," analyses"," of"," power"," spectrum"," and"," bis","pec","trum","\n\n","The"," gravitational"," force"," plays"," a"," crucial"," role"," in"," understanding"," the"," formation"," and"," evolution"," of"," the"," universe","."," Newton","'","s"," law"," of"," universal"," gravitation"," provides"," an"," excellent"," description"," of"," the"," gravitational"," force"," at"," small"," scales",","," but"," it"," fails"," to"," provide"," an"," accurate"," description"," of"," the"," behavior"," of"," the"," gravitational"," force"," at"," cosmological"," scales","."," Violations"," of"," Newton","'","s"," law"," at"," large"," scales"," can"," have"," significant"," implications"," for"," our"," understanding"," of"," the"," universe",","," and"," thus",","," it"," is"," essential"," to"," constrain"," these"," deviations","."," In"," this"," work",","," we"," utilize"," galaxy"," clustering"," data"," to"," constrain"," these"," deviations",".","\n\n","We"," have"," employed"," a"," perturb","ative"," and"," numerical"," approach"," to"," analyze"," the"," power"," spectrum"," and"," bis","pec","trum"," of"," the"," galaxy"," distribution","."," Our"," key"," methodology"," has"," been"," to"," compare"," the"," predicted"," galaxy"," power"," spectrum"," and"," bis","pec","trum"," from"," different"," gravitational"," force"," models"," to"," the"," observed"," data","."," We"," have"," found"," significant"," differences"," between"," the"," predictions"," of"," the"," power"," spectrum"," and"," bis","pec","trum"," from"," Newtonian"," gravity"," and"," those"," from"," modified"," gravity"," models",","," such"," as"," the"," one"," proposed"," by"," MOND","."," These"," differences"," have"," been"," used"," to"," constrain"," the"," deviations"," from"," Newtonian"," gravity"," at"," cosmological"," scales","."," Our"," results"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," observed"," galaxy"," clustering"," data"," can"," be"," used"," to"," constrain"," the"," deviations"," from"," Newtonian"," gravity",","," providing"," valuable"," insight"," into"," the"," nature"," of"," the"," gravitational"," force"," at"," cosmological"," scales","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}